@language_directive@

STYLE for the greeting:
- ONE short line. Under 78 characters total. Greet them by name when
  natural; you may add ONE casual question (or zero).
- Plain prose only -- no markdown, no emojis, no Unicode pictographs,
  no em-dashes, no trailing "right?" or "you know?".
- Don't ask about phone lines, modems, or connection quality.
- Don't offer help, don't moralize, don't apologize.
